    "description": "A synthetic surface treatment preservative sprayed or applied to citrus fruit peels to prevent mold during shipping. One of the few food additives applied EXTERNALLY to food, not mixed in. BANNED in Australia despite EU/USA approval. Must be washed off before consuming citrus peel (zest). NOT intended to be eaten - remains on outer surface only."
  },
